# Project Documentation

## Project Name
Python Hello World

## Description
This project is a simple Python application created for the Week 7 GitHub assignment.

## Files Included
- main.py
- hello.txt
- README.md
- Documentation.md
- Contributing.md
- License.md

## How to Run

```bash
python main.py
```

## Features
- Displays a greeting message.
- Demonstrates a simple addition function.
- Uses GitHub for version control.
- Includes a GitHub Actions workflow for automation.
